class Solution {
    public int minPartitions(String n) {
        int max = 0;
        for (char c : n.toCharArray()) {
            max = Math.max(max, c - '0');
        }
        return max;
    }
}
```
efficiency: HIGH
time complexity: O(n)
space complexity: O(1)
energy implications: LOW
explanation: The solution iterates through each character in the string, keeping track of the maximum digit encountered, which directly corresponds to the minimum number of deci-binary numbers needed to sum up to the given number.

